{"tid":1632850,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"裝修鄉議局手足俾大公點了相 快做準備","createTime":"2019-10-07T00:05:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T01:08:56.000Z","uid":72009,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c8201cd8ada01201f2d2b48631e3f22d63d4dfd0","tid":1632850,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T00:05:04.000Z","msg":"　　一批暴徒昨晚快閃破壞十八鄉鄉事委員會，將三個汽油彈掟到二樓，引起火警，大公報記者在現場直擊，發現暴徒約在11時半分頭逃竄躲避警察。其中五男四女到鳳庭苑B座華庭閣外的建業街，鬼鬼祟祟換衫，有人問是否有車可順路載離開。九男女之後到附近的新記雞粥舖，施施然宵夜，到約12時半開始分批離開，一架七人車到場接載。暴徒逃離的全過程相當嫻熟，明顯有組織、有計劃。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.takungpao.com.hk/231106/2019/1006/358143.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.takungpao.com.hk%2F231106%2F2019%2F1006%2F358143.html&d=QZYHYFPECKJw76TN47EEpmWjTds15DFTxBM9bbMqy3g%3D&h=cc9e0e81\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.takungpao.com.hk/231106/2019/1006/358143.html</a><br />\n<br />\nlink冇相，但報紙好像有，見香討有相，清楚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家辦完大事建議即散，仲去宵夜，太容易俾人捉到，手足快清電腦！"},{"pid":"b3dd107f44c84670e04f6398c577dca83e9e4092","tid":1632850,"uid":33868,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T00:06:25.000Z","msg":"都唔知係唔係<br />\n仲要有七人車接走，係唔係Mazda Biante <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6561739df38e3598b8487dcc1cf0db0f2773b771","tid":1632850,"uid":72009,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b3dd107f44c84670e04f6398c577dca83e9e4092","tid":1632850,"uid":33868,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T00:06:25.000Z","msg":"都唔知係唔係<br />\n仲要有七人車接走，係唔係Mazda Biante <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T00:09:59.000Z","msg":"希望唔係，幅相好清楚，我怕佢地俾鄉黑尋仇"},{"pid":"dbb4aef10edc6c062ca4c88056fe3a8b7ef8cf48","tid":1632850,"uid":288523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T00:37:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c53847f64e7d5032398842a7154a0ab5ad1766b3","t